I"<ol>
  <li>Some packages in <code class="highlighter-rouge">devel_basis</code> pattern like <code class="highlighter-rouge">gcc</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">make</code>, etc. are needed so we should install it first.
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo zypper in -t pattern devel_basis
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>After that, we should install <code class="highlighter-rouge">ruby-devel</code> package.
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo zypper in ruby-devel
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Then you can install any Ruby gems such as <code class="highlighter-rouge">jekyll</code></li>
</ol>

